<p>The work is structural and unglamorous. Schema, snippets, entities, freshness, sources, tables. Done once correctly across your top 20 commercial pages, the effect compounds for years.</p>
<p>The brands that move on this in 2026 are the brands that show up in 2027 when a buyer opens Claude and asks "which one should I pick."</p>
